            <title>[LU-11772] patchless-ldiskfs-server build for MOFED</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-11772</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Hello,&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&#160;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;I discovered today with the release of 2.10.6 that there are now builds of lustre against the latest MOFED available on downloads.whamcloud.com.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;The non-MOFED builds are available as client, server and&#160;patchless-ldiskfs-server, but the MOFED builds only provide client and server.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&#160;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Would it be possible to also generate a&#160;patchless-ldiskfs-server build of the MOFED version ?&lt;/p&gt;</description>
